ZH: 我们应该忘掉过去的烦恼。
EN: We should forget about the troubles of the past.

ZH: 请忘掉我刚才说的话。
EN: Please forget what I just said.

ZH: 我们不能忘掉这次机会。
EN: We cannot forget about this opportunity.

ZH: 忘掉我的过错，将就一下吧。
EN: Forget my mistake, please just let it go.

ZH: 他忘掉了自己的生日。
EN: He forgot his own birthday.

ZH: 这事已经发生了太久，我们都应该忘掉了。
EN: This matter happened too long ago, we should all have forgotten about it now.

ZH: 我们不能忘掉每日的努力。
EN: We should not forget our daily efforts.

ZH: 对不起，我应该忘掉你的过错。
EN: I'm sorry, I should forget about your mistake.

ZH: 我已经完全忘掉了那个人的名字。
EN: I have completely forgotten that person's name.

ZH: 请忘掉我的过去，只看重现在。
EN: Please forget my past and focus on the present.

ZH: 我们不能忘掉他们的付出。
EN: We must not forget their contributions.

ZH: 这些回忆让我无法忘掉。
EN: These memories make it hard for me to forget.

ZH: 忘掉昨天，珍惜今天。
EN: Forget about yesterday, cherish today.

ZH: 我真的希望能忘掉那段痛苦的经历。
EN: I really hope to forget that painful experience.

